  <brief_title>Time-dependent Improvement of Functional Outcome Following LCS Rotating Platform TKR</brief_title>
  <official_title>Time-dependent Improvement of Functional Outcome Following LCS Rotating Platform TKR - A Prospective Longitudinal Study With Repetitive Measures of KOOS</official_title>
